description: Retrieves a random word from external api by asking for a word, or you can optionally request a random (X) letter word to get a random word of the specified length (supports 3-20 character length)
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask random vocab a word
Alexa ask random vocab a random word
Alexa ask random vocab an eight letter word
name: RandomVocab
shortDescription: request a random word with optional parameter 3-20 characters length
